      <title>Jupyter Notebook更改储存路径及汉化工具栏、安装插件的方法</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/15/jupyter-notebook-bu-fen-wen-ti-jie-jue-fang-an/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/15/jupyter-notebook-bu-fen-wen-ti-jie-jue-fang-an/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="Jupyter-Notebook更改储存路径及汉化工具栏、安装插件的方法"><a href="#Jupyter-Notebook更改储存路径及汉化工具栏、安装插件的方法" class="headerlink" title="Jupyter Notebook更改储存路径及汉化工具栏、安装插件的方法"></a>Jupyter Notebook更改储存路径及汉化工具栏、安装插件的方法</h2><h3 id="更改储存路径"><a href="#更改储存路径" class="headerlink" title="更改储存路径"></a>更改储存路径</h3><ol><li>找到配置文件–jupyter_notebook_config.py</li></ol><ul><li>对应路径：<code>C:\Users\用户名\.jupyter\jupyter_notebook_config.py</code></li><li>使用相应工具打开，如：’’记事本’’、’’Notepad++’’等</li></ul><ol start="2"><li>更改配置</li></ol><ul><li>找到<code>#c.NotebookApp.notebook_dir = &#39; &#39;</code>,使用”查找”功能更加快捷</li><li>找到该语句后，<strong>删掉’#’及其后空白</strong>，将准备好的储存路径填入单引号中，保存配置即可</li><li>在开始菜单中找到”Jupyte Notebook”快捷方式，’’右击–&gt;更多–&gt;打开文件位置’’</li><li>找到对应的快捷方式图标，’’右击–&gt;属性–&gt;目标’’，删掉最后的<code>%USERPROFILE%/</code>,<strong>点击”应用”、”确定”保存配置</strong></li><li>关闭已打开的”Jupyte Notebook”，重新启动即可</li></ul><h3 id="汉化工具栏"><a href="#汉化工具栏" class="headerlink" title="汉化工具栏"></a>汉化工具栏</h3><ol><li><p>打开搜索，输入环境变量（如图），点击即可 <img src="C:\Users\20349\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210815111841318.png" alt="image-20210815111841318"></p></li><li><p>在弹窗中点击：”高级”–&gt;”环境变量”</p><p><img src="C:\Users\20349\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210815112445845.png" alt="image-20210815112445845"></p></li><li><p>点击<strong>用户变量</strong>，选择”新建”</p></li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">变量名：<span class="token environment constant">LANG</span>变量值：zh_CN.UTF8<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="C:\Users\20349\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210815113055427.png" alt="image-20210815113055427" style="zoom:80%;" /><ol start="4"><li>点击确定保存即可</li></ol><h3 id="安装扩展插件"><a href="#安装扩展插件" class="headerlink" title="安装扩展插件"></a>安装扩展插件</h3><ol><li><p>安装Jupyter Notebook扩展包</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">pip <span class="token function">install</span> jupyter_contrib_nbextensionsjupyter contrib nbextension <span class="token function">install</span> --user<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ol><ol start="2"><li>启动Jupyter Notebook,工具栏中多出一个选项“Nbextensions”即为成功</li></ol><img src="C:\Users\20349\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210815114536864.png" alt="image-20210815114536864" style="zoom:80%;" /><ol start="3"><li>推荐开启的插件：</li></ol><ul><li>Table of Contents  : 根据你所写的标题自动生成目录</li><li>Variable Inspector : 变量追踪</li><li>Code perttify : 代码格式化</li><li>Collapsible headings : 标题折叠</li><li>ExecuteTime : 显示代码运行耗时</li><li>Autopep8 : 一键美化</li><li>Toggle all line numbers : 显示行号</li><li>Skip-traceback ：跳过回溯</li><li>Hide code ：隐藏输入，仅展示输出</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
